<item>
            <title>[PIG-2221] Couldnt find documentation for ColumnMapKeyPrune optimization rule</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2221</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are no documentations for some of the Optimization Rules, &lt;br/&gt;
For ex; ColumnMapKeyPrune&lt;br/&gt;
in &lt;a href=&quot;http://pig.apache.org/docs/r0.8.1/piglatin_ref1.html#Optimization+Rules&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://pig.apache.org/docs/r0.8.1/piglatin_ref1.html#Optimization+Rules&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And moreover I believe the documentaion should be saying how to disable these rules using -t option. &lt;br/&gt;
It would be nice if the documentation could talk of some uses cases where it makes sense to disable the optimization rule. &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
